metadata.name: Montaigne 1/1
metadata.description:
Clued up on cast-iron architecture, Belgian block pavement, sweeping galleries and textile manufacturing city workshops. Available for industrial development, garment production, pattern engineering. Traditional floral print puffer jacket, exaggerated high collar and long sleeves. Short eggshell blue denim skirt, violet couture round neck long sleeve bodysuit. 

Synth Graph: a center front view portrait, 2012, photograph of a beautiful tanned female model wearing a detailed red floral printed purple and red puffy jacket, with a ripped denim miniskirt, black high top sneakers, bright orange socks, blue hair, red lipstick, walking down manhattan in the 2000s, highly detailed. Sampler: plms, steps: 75, scale: 11.
